overview: Go ahead and gorge yourself on this triple whammy. Master director Bruce Cam’s yearly outdoor feature brings leather legend Ray Dragon back to the screen, unforgettably paired with TITAN’s legend-in-the-making, Dred Scott. After a scene crammed with stunning and sweaty reversals, these monumental guys are joined by seven other rough and rugged TITANMen on the towering cliffs of the upper Grand Canyon! A primitive and majestic setting that’s the embodiment of TITAN masculinity.
title: Gorge
